{"tid":1334042,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【滿手鮮血】任達華遭兇徒持利刀猛刺腹部","createTime":"2019-07-20T03:32:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T10:31:44.000Z","uid":68738,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1306139058ac2c6f4be15e5308320084263eb22d","tid":1334042,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190720/photo/bkn-20190720110712717-0720_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190720112120\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190720%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190720110712717-0720_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190720112120&h=00785439&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港藝人任達華到內地中山出席活動時，當他站在台上時，突然有人身穿灰色背心的男子上台，隨後從褲袋拿出利刀，對着任達華的肚部猛刺，隨後更不停揮刀追斬任，任達華不停閃避，現場人員即時衝上前制服疑兇，任達華手按着腹部，白色襯衣明顯有血漬，但他狀態清醒，由一眾人員送下送往醫院接受治療。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190720/mobile/bkn-20190720110712717-0720_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190720%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190720110712717-0720_00862_001.html&d=JxnBaozbJlL%2F%2BfT%2BMtMvbseYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=f47c426f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190720/mobile/bkn-20190720110712717-0720_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"43aa8c2f0e1a4e36195912fcfce0cff290b47b35","tid":1334042,"uid":38904,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:34:33.000Z","msg":"希望可以傷重不治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0f05c22a3cd6c31c386ad1ae292096a7cde3a25","tid":1334042,"uid":238013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:44:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">PTU</span>"},{"pid":"f666871988e6fbf359eacf552023a70023dccb60","tid":1334042,"uid":87272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T03:49:18.000Z","msg":"撚有滿手咩 失敗"